-*- texinfo -*-
@deftypefn {Mapping Function} {} abs (@var{z})
Compute the magnitude of @var{z}, defined as
@iftex
@tex
$|z| = \sqrt{x^2 + y^2}$.
@end tex
@end iftex
@ifinfo
|@var{z}| = @code{sqrt (x^2 + y^2)}.
@end ifinfo

For example,

@example
@group
abs (3 + 4i)
     @result{} 5
@end group
@end example
@end deftypefn
